content:
The Order Checkbook service process allows your customers to order a checkbook. Customers can choose the number of checks required and the delivery mode while ordering.

Available in: Lightning Experience, Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited Editions where Financial Services Cloud is enabled.

Use Service Process Studio to enable the Order Checkbook service process for agents to capture new checkbook orders.
Your service agents can submit a new checkbook request through the Order Checkbook OmniScript, creating a case in Salesforce.
title: Order Checkbook Service Process Guide
